OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,FBoth energy suppliers have said that
OL,7,Fthe increase is due to higher global
OL,8,Fenergy prices as a result of the
OL,9,Fongoing conflict in the Middle East.
OL,11,FThe Utility Regulator confirmed that a
OL,12,Freview of the tariffs was carried out
OL,13,Fin early May resulting in an annual
OL,14,Frise of #64 for Power NI's domestic
OL,15,Felectricity customers.
OL,17,FHouseholds and small businesses in the
OL,18,FTen Towns area on Firmus Energy's gas
OL,19,Ftariff will also see a #134 increase
OL,20,Fin their yearly bill.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
