CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,FSSE Airtricity's regulated gas tariff
OL,7,Fin the Greater Belfast Area has not
OL,8,Fbeen part of this review but will be
OL,9,Fincluded in a review process that will
OL,10,Fbegin in August, in advance of a
OL,11,Fpossible October 1 change.
OL,13,FLeigh Greer, Head of Security of
OL,14,FSupply and Markets Regulation at the
OL,15,FUtility Regulator said: "We understand
OL,16,Fthis increase in energy costs is not
OL,17,Fwelcome news for consumers.
OL,26,@wD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, the impact of
OL,7,Fcontinued and sustained rises in the
OL,8,Fwholesale cost of energy, caused by
OL,9,Fthe conflict in the Middle East, has
OL,10,Fresulted in these increases.
OL,12,F"The conflict has impacted energy
OL,13,Fprices globally, and has already
OL,14,Faffected home heating oil, petrol and
OL,15,Fdiesel prices.
OL,17,F"Our regulation ensures that the
OL,18,Fprices consumers pay reflect the
OL,19,Funderlying wholesale costs and the
OL,20,Factual costs of supplying energy to
OL,21,Fyour home.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
