FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,F"If you are worried about paying for
OL,7,Fyour electricity or gas, there is help
OL,8,Favailable. We would encourage you to
OL,9,Fcontact your supplier in the first
OL,10,Finstance, to make them aware of your
OL,11,Fcircumstances, and discuss the options
OL,12,Favailable.
OL,14,F"In addition, there are a number of
OL,15,Fagencies who can provide free and
OL,16,Findependent advice to households,
OL,17,Fincluding Advice NI, Christians
OL,18,FAgainst Poverty, the Consumer Council
OL,19,Fand Money and Pensions Service's
OL,20,FMoneyHelper."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
