CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, we continue to
OL,7,Fexperience elevated wholesale prices
OL,8,Fwhile the conflict in the Middle East
OL,9,Fremains unresolved.
OL,11,F"Over the last year or so we have
OL,12,Freduced our tariffs on three separate
OL,13,Foccasions, bringing tariffs down by
OL,14,Fover 27% and saving customers around
OL,15,F#300 on average per annum.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
