PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780085152
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise for Power NI and
OL,4,CFirmus customers
OL,6,F"Today's announcement, whilst
OL,7,Funwelcome, means that customers' bills
OL,8,Fwill now be roughly the same as this
OL,9,Ftime last year and still significantly
OL,10,Fbelow where they had been in previous
OL,11,Fyears."
